{"tid":130273,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"至索星二代沈月 跌膊襯厚底靴好貼潮","createTime":"2017-02-22T09:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T18:50:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58ae862564b1c4fc079ad72613504f84115f6d39","tid":130273,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"至索星二代沈月<br />\n跌膊襯厚底靴好貼潮<br />\n<br />\n13,773<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n時裝王國I.T老闆沈嘉偉與邱淑貞的15歲囡囡沈月，盡得媽咪優良DNA，樣子生得非常標緻，愈大愈靚女，絕對稱得上是索星二代。<br />\n<br />\n年紀輕輕的沈月已經著盡靚衫，所以好有時裝品味。近期愈來愈活躍於社交平台的她，日前連環上載了三張靚相，身穿超厚底platform boots，再加一件跌膊恤衫大晒香肩，以及搭配choker，造型時尚有潮味，加上回眸一笑絕對係無得輸。超厚底的platform boots深受潮人追捧，阿徐、Kary和Hebe都分別穿過Balenciaga推出的款式，而潮人最buy的Vetements，亦有類近款式。<br />\n<br />\n更多時尚、美容新聞，即上：<a href=\"http://add.appledaily.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fadd.appledaily.com&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=eaec0848\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fadd.appledaily.com&h=412cf5ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://add.appledaily.com</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n明哥難頂劉以達肚腩<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n阿佘同子華七年之癢"},{"pid":"180fdd36ae826cb493b0e6d0af28074c21938786","tid":130273,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170222/org/1487703101_0a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170222%2Forg%2F1487703101_0a44.jpg&h=66cc1068&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e3dc8c1f2bb6d659e8df78ecfeb5d80f7ef4a34","tid":130273,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"得老母七成到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小母狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c039391b15df2bc93162c9fc961ea7083b9d94f3","tid":130273,"uid":35430